Free online furigana literature?
by Kenitai » Thu 03.04.2010 4:12 pm Hi,I've been wondering if there's any Japanese/English websites that provide free literature, using furigana?Or, if there's a program to instantly evoke furigana from kanji in a bunch of Japanese web literature.Just to prepare for my future university studies... Cheers,Kenitai
